{"word":"τρυφάω","slug":"τρυφάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n105738\" key=\"trufa/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">τρῠφάω</orth>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">τρυφή</etym>) <sense id=\"n105738.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">live softly, luxuriously, fare sumptuously,</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐν ἀγκάλαις μητρὸς τρυφῆσαι,</foreign> of a child, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg010.perseus-grc1:1376\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ion\">Ion</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1376</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg017.perseus-grc1:969\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ba.\">Ba.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">969</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τ. ἐν ταῖς ἐσθῆσι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0010.tlg013.perseus-grc1:32\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Isoc.\">Isoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.32</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τ. καὶ μεγαλοπρεπῶς διαιτᾶσθαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg015.perseus-grc1:1:11\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ath.\">Ath.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.11</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">λευκὸς ἄνθρωπος, παχύς, ἀργός . . , εἰωθὼς τρυφᾶν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:ct